# AI Chat Assistant with Memory

## Project Overview

Developed an intelligent conversational AI assistant using **n8n Cloud** and **Google Gemini** to demonstrate AI workflow automation and context-aware conversations. The assistant accepts user messages through a chat interface, generates natural language responses using a large language model (LLM), and maintains conversation context with memory for a more personalized user experience.

## Key Features

* Designed an AI-powered chatbot using n8n's AI Agent architecture.
* Integrated Google Gemini as the primary large language model.
* Implemented conversational memory to maintain context across multiple interactions.
* Configured a Chat Trigger for real-time user communication.
* Customized the AI Agent with system instructions to control behavior and response quality.
* Tested and validated workflow execution through n8n Cloud's chat interface.

## Technologies Used

* n8n Cloud
* Google Gemini API
* AI Agent
* Chat Trigger
* Simple Memory
* Prompt Engineering

## Skills Demonstrated

* AI Workflow Automation
* Large Language Model (LLM) Integration
* Conversational AI Development
* Prompt Engineering
* Workflow Design
* Context Management with AI Memory
* Automation Testing and Debugging

## Outcome

Successfully built and deployed a functional AI chat assistant capable of engaging in natural conversations while retaining contextual information throughout a session. This project demonstrates foundational skills in designing AI-powered automation workflows using n8n and modern LLM technologies.
